title: Nature Organic Cafe
description: Re:Nature is what the signage says. Small place with Wi-Fi est. 2016 at 神宮前3-23-6. Directions: from Takeshita Dori walk until you reach the large street at the end, across the street there's a light green building called Moshi Moshi Box which is the Harajuku Information Center, around two doors to the left of this building there's its signage and a white spiral staircase, climb all the way to the top until you reach a terrace.
